+    You can specify a ``key_transform`` callable to format the
+    ``grouper`` value used for display, without changing how items are
+    grouped.
+
+    .. sourcecode:: jinja
+
+        <ul>{% for month, items in users|groupby("signup_date", key_transform=format_month) %}
+          <li>{{ month }}: {{ items|map(attribute="name")|join(", ") }}</li>
+        {% endfor %}</ul>
+
+    .. versionchanged:: 3.1
+        Added the ``key_transform`` parameter.
+
     .. versionchanged:: 3.0
         Added the ``default`` parameter.
 
